# Next.js Full-Stack Boilerplate Generation

Generate a production-ready Next.js 14+ boilerplate from scratch following the specs in [context.md](file:///home/seno/Public/Project/next-js-boilerplate/context.md).

## Proposed Changes

### Phase 1: Project Initialization
- Initialize Next.js with `npx create-next-app@latest` (TypeScript, App Router, Tailwind CSS, ESLint)
- Install deps: Prisma, NextAuth v5, TanStack Query, Zustand, next-themes, react-hook-form, zod, @hookform/resolvers, sonner, lucide-react
- Init shadcn/ui and install components (Button, Input, Card, Dialog, Tabs, Form, Sonner)

### Phase 2: Database & Prisma
#### [NEW] `prisma/schema.prisma`
- User, Account, Session, VerificationToken models (NextAuth-compatible)
- Role enum (USER, ADMIN), createdAt/updatedAt on all models

#### [NEW] `src/lib/db.ts`
- Prisma Client singleton pattern

### Phase 3: Authentication
#### [NEW] `src/lib/auth.ts` — NextAuth.js config with Prisma Adapter
#### [NEW] `src/middleware.ts` — Protect `/dashboard/:path*`
#### [NEW] `src/components/providers/session-provider.tsx` — SessionProvider wrapper

### Phase 4: Architecture & Providers
#### [NEW] `src/components/providers/query-provider.tsx` — TanStack Query
#### [NEW] `src/components/providers/theme-provider.tsx` — next-themes
#### [NEW] `src/components/providers/index.tsx` — Combined providers wrapper
#### [NEW] `src/types/index.ts` — Shared TypeScript interfaces

### Phase 5: UI/UX
- shadcn/ui components installed via CLI
#### [NEW] `src/components/shared/navbar.tsx` — Nav with dark mode toggle
#### [NEW] `src/components/shared/footer.tsx`
#### [NEW] `src/components/shared/form-input.tsx` — react-hook-form + zod integration
#### [NEW] `src/components/shared/theme-toggle.tsx` — Dark mode toggle button

### Phase 6: API & Data Fetching
#### [NEW] `src/actions/profile.ts` — Example Server Action for "Profile Update"
#### [NEW] `src/lib/validations/profile.ts` — Zod schema for profile

### Phase 7: Infrastructure & SEO
#### [NEW] `docker-compose.yml` — PostgreSQL + pgAdmin
#### [NEW] `src/lib/metadata.ts` — Dynamic meta/OG helper
#### [NEW] `.env.example` — Placeholder env vars

### Phase 8: Pages & Layouts
#### [MODIFY] `src/app/layout.tsx` — Wrap with providers, add fonts
#### [MODIFY] `src/app/page.tsx` — Landing page
#### [NEW] `src/app/dashboard/page.tsx` — Protected dashboard page
#### [NEW] `src/app/auth/signin/page.tsx` — Sign-in page

### Phase 9: Documentation
#### [NEW] `README.md` — Setup, migrations, local vs Supabase instructions

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Run `npx prisma validate` to verify schema
- Run `npm run build` to ensure the project compiles without errors

### Manual Verification
- Run `npm run dev` and open `http://localhost:3000` — verify homepage renders
- Check dark mode toggle works
- Verify `/dashboard` redirects to sign-in when unauthenticated
